snippet.title: Amber Heard claps back at Johnny   altering his tattoo tribute to her
snippet.description:
Amber Heard just shut down her ex-husband Johnny Depp with one Instagram photo.
[time]The actress seemingly shaded the 55-year-old's knuckle tattoo, Slim, which he got as a tribute to her when they were still married. But since their 2016 split, Depp has had the ink reworked twice, so it went from 'Slim' to 'Scum' and, most recently, 'Scam.'
